OM parameter values

This was part of the simulation study addressing the effect of the magnitude of catchability variation.

  • Base catchability: \(0.2\)
  • Marginal SD of commercial log-catchability deviations: \(0.001\)
  • Marginal SD of survey log-catchability deviations: \(0\)
  • Preference power: \(1\)
